<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>غَلِيظٍ <span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢٨- وَما تَفَرَّقُوا إِلَّا مِنْ بَعْدِ ما جاءَهُمُ الْعِلْمُ بَغْياً بَيْنَهُمْ وَلَوْلا كَلِمَةٌ سَبَقَتْ مِنْ رَبِّكَ إِلى أَجَلٍ مُسَمًّى لَقُضِيَ بَيْنَهُمْ وَإِنَّ الَّذِينَ أُورِثُوا الْكِتابَ مِنْ بَعْدِهِمْ لَفِي شَكٍّ مِنْهُ مُرِيبٍ <span class="c2">(١٤)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢٩- وَنادى فِرْعَوْنُ فِي قَوْمِهِ قالَ يا قَوْمِ أَلَيْسَ لِي مُلْكُ مِصْرَ وَهذِهِ الْأَنْهارُ تَجْرِي مِنْ تَحْتِي أَفَلا تُبْصِرُونَ <span class="c2">(٥١)</span> <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٣٠- أَكُفَّارُكُمْ خَيْرٌ مِنْ أُولئِكُمْ أَمْ لَكُمْ بَراءَةٌ فِي الزُّبُرِ <span class="c2">(٤٣)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَمْ يَقُولُونَ نَحْنُ جَمِيعٌ مُنْتَصِرٌ <span class="c2">(٤٤)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>سَيُهْزَمُ الْجَمْعُ وَيُوَلُّونَ الدُّبُرَ <span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> <span class="c2">«٤»</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٣١- ما أَغْنى عَنِّي مالِيَهْ <span class="c2">(٢٨)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>هَلَكَ عَنِّي سُلْطانِيَهْ <span class="c2">(٢٩)</span> <span class="c2">«٥»</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٣٢- قالَ نُوحٌ رَبِّ إِنَّهُمْ عَصَوْنِي وَاتَّبَعُوا مَنْ لَمْ يَزِدْهُ مالُهُ وَوَلَدُهُ إِلَّا خَساراً <span class="c2">(٢١)</span> <span class="c2">«٦»</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٣٣- ذَرْنِي وَمَنْ خَلَقْتُ وَحِيداً <span class="c2">(١١)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَجَعَلْتُ لَهُ مالًا مَمْدُوداً <span class="c2">(١٢)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَبَنِينَ شُهُوداً <span class="c2">(١٣)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَمَهَّدْتُ لَهُ تَمْهِيداً <span class="c2">(١٤)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>ثُمَّ يَطْمَعُ أَنْ أَزِيدَ <span class="c2">(١٥)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>كَلَّا إِنَّهُ كانَ لِآياتِنا عَنِيداً <span class="c2">(١٦)</span> <span class="c2">«٧»</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٣٤- أَيَحْسَبُ أَنْ لَنْ يَقْدِرَ عَلَيْهِ أَحَدٌ <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>يَقُولُ أَهْلَكْتُ مالًا لُبَداً <span class="c2">(٦)</span> <span class="c2">«٨»</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٣٥- وَيْلٌ لِكُلِّ هُمَزَةٍ لُمَزَةٍ <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>الَّذِي جَمَعَ مالًا وَعَدَّدَهُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>يَحْسَبُ أَنَّ مالَهُ أَخْلَدَهُ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>كَلَّا لَيُنْبَذَنَّ فِي الْحُطَمَةِ <span class="c2">(٤)</span> <span class="c2">«٩»</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>٣٦- تَبَّتْ يَدا أَبِي لَهَبٍ وَتَبَّ <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>ما أَغْنى عَنْهُ مالُهُ وَما كَسَبَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>سَيَصْلى ناراً ذاتَ لَهَبٍ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>وَامْرَأَتُهُ حَمَّالَةَ الْحَطَبِ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>فِي جِيدِها حَبْلٌ مِنْ مَسَدٍ <span class="c2">(٥)</span> <span class="c2">«١٠»</span><a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
